{"tid":105748,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 6 Plus 又出現起火事件","createTime":"2017-02-03T06:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T05:41:03.000Z","uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c53905c1b57be2433eceb8ffff69e49d225ca1df","tid":105748,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T06:34:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">iPhone 6 Plus 又出現起火事件</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/iphone-6P-explode-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fiphone-6P-explode-1.jpg&h=df0e194f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在手機的安全性似乎在精密度不斷提高下似乎變得越來越不可靠，之前 Galaxy Note 7 就因不斷自燃爆炸成為手機界的焦點，現在輪到死對頭 iPhone 也出自燃事故。<br />\n<br />\n日前有報導指在美國佛羅里達州的一名叫 Amada 的女性在睡夢中發現在床頭櫃上充著電的 iPhone 6 Plus 不知不覺間起火並產生濃煙。她表示  &ldquo;我的臉和手機離得很近，它突然起火後火苗竄起來，把我弄醒，幸好我是一個睡得不沉的人。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n結果是床頭櫃被燒毀，而她的枕頭、被和窗簾也被燒了一點。Amada 更說如果不是她丈夫醒了後立即把手機上的火撲滅，整個窗簾也會燒著，後果嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n不過原來她鄰居 Greg Miceli 出現同樣情況，但程度更嚴重，因為他的 iPhone 6 Plus 雖然同樣放在床邊，但<span style=\"color: red;\">手機當時並是沒有充電！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有指 Apple 已經和 Amada 聯繫，並表示將調查這事故並為她提供一部新 iPhone，<span style=\"color: red;\">同時更指只要將起火的 iPhone 6 Plus 交給 Apple 便會賠償 749 美元。</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/iphone-6P-explode1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fiphone-6P-explode1.png&h=e642525d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/iphone-6P-explode2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fiphone-6P-explode2.jpg&h=15505da0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/iphone-6P-explode3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fiphone-6P-explode3.jpg&h=d9fa5d3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/iphone-6P-explode4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fiphone-6P-explode4.jpg&h=d33f5427&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5c5e938a1e4862919b6afb15e13e40155c82e0e","tid":105748,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719988933d86f1f24ce0f4df57328e3989847c61","tid":105748,"uid":70962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"仲提供新iPhone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw,個處理幾好,有即時賠償"},{"pid":"ffce39c2ffbc7d53879200c8c95bbdf3924115d2","tid":105748,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲提供新iPhone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw,個處理幾好,有即時賠償</blockquote><br />\n冇錯，雖然報爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}